1. *Osumnjičeni* je priveden na ispitivanje. (The suspect was brought in for questioning.)
2. Policija traga za *osumnjičenim* koji je pobegao. (The police are searching for the suspect who escaped.)
3. *Osumnjičenog* su optužili za ubistvo. (The suspect was accused of murder.)
4. Advokat brani *osumnjičenog* u sudnici. (The lawyer is defending the suspect in the courtroom.)
5. Inspektor je saslušao sve *osumnjičene* u vezi sa slučajem. (The inspector questioned all the suspects related to the case.)
6. Postoje indicije da je *osumnjičeni* umesan u kriminalnu organizaciju. (There are indications that the suspect is involved in a criminal organization.)
7. *Osumnjičeni* je negirao krivicu tokom ispitivanja. (The suspect denied guilt during questioning.)
8. Sud je pustio *osumnjičenog* uz kauciju. (The court released the suspect on bail.)